name: WebStorm
description:
WebStorm is a JavaScript IDE. It is featured with intelligent coding assistance, latest technology and framework support, version control system integration, commissioning, tracking, testing and so on. Meanwhile, typescript compiler is built in, hundreds of project module and other functions are integrated.
You need to get the licence to use this version.

zh_CN.description:
WebStorm是一个开发JavaScript的集成开发环境，它具有智能编码辅助、支持最新技术和框架、集成版本控制系统、调试，跟踪和测试等功能，同时内置了打字稿编译器、整合数以百计的项目模板等其他功能。
该版本需要您自行购买长期使用授权。
